itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜撚野黎?柒撚獴獴?"},{"pid":"f5f312129948cba80d7904d76844ae058d039f73","tid":1678150,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=f88768dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=6c6f94a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=92315bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"f519e52a5dbe563ad4f133ed4c6381901b50c8c0","tid":1678150,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 11 &middot; 2 </span><br />\n求援國際 堅守自治</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園流水式集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期六 11 &middot; 9 </span><br />\n柏林圍牆倒塌30周年集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:30 中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【行動Post】11月活動集合：拋磚引玉</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678327</a>"},{"pid":"47baf93676b9f303a4084e694b394b14ac0de67b","tid":1678150,"uid":124247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re